        <div class="jumbotron  pt-4">
            <div class="col-lg-12 col-md-12 col-sm-12">
                <h2 class="text-center">
                    PROVIDING URBAN FACILITIES IN THE RURAL AREAS
                </h2>
                <hr />
                <p>
                    Inspired by the Book written by Dr APJ Abdul Kalam namely Providing Urban Facilities In The Rural Areas Founder of Saroj Seva Sansthan, Lt Col Manmohan Thakur spent his hard earned money to create Urban Facilities in his Remote Village Baghnocha, Vaishali in Bihar, in the fond memory of his Late Mother  Smt Saroj Devi. The multipurpose Community Hall is equipped with the following infrastructure.
                </p>
                <ol>
                    <li>
                        Hall with Vitrified Tiles and concrete roof with Capacity of 300 persons.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        Two Rooms for office and Computer Room.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        Modern Furniture for children.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        LED TV.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        Books from Delhi Schools and Coaching Centres.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        Electricity Fans and Inverter.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        Sports facilities in the Campus.
                    </li>
                </ol>
                <p>
                    There is a need to curb migration of people from Villages to the Cities which are overcrowded. If all the facilities of Cities are made available in the Villages, people will prefer staying in villages, as nature is more environment friendly in rural areas as compared to the Cities and Towns.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    </div>
    <div class="row bg-dark">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="text-white pt-4 pb-4">
                <div class="col-lg-12 col-md-12 col-sm-12">
                    <h2 class="text-right">GIVING BACK TO THE SOCIETY</h2>
                    <hr style="border-top:1px solid #ccc;" />
                    <p>
                        <img class="float-md-right float-sm-none m-md-2 mt-md-0 img-thumbnail" style="max-width: 370px; width: 100%;" src="~/Content/Images/GIVING_BACK.jpg" />
                        It is quite disheartening to see that people once move to the Cities, disconnect themselves from the Society and Village they belong to.  As a result the people who supported them during their struggle period do not receive any things back from them.  Their contribution is forgotten.  This step is to reconnect with the Root where we belong to.  Our village needs guidance and support.  Innocent children do not know how to go about studies and make a Career.  It is our moral responsibility to guide them, teach them and help them achieve their Goal. It will help us achieve Overall development of our Society and Nation as a whole.
                    </p>
