                        <img class="float-md-right float-sm-none m-md-2 mt-md-0 img-thumbnail" style="max-width: 370px; width: 100%;" src="~/Content/Images/HEALTH_CARE_1.png" />
                        Generally people are careless about their health in villages. They are not aware what to eat what not to eat in case of any disease. Most of the diseases can be prevented/curbed just by regular exercises and walk. The Sansthan conducts Medical Camp time to time to conduct free check up. Any villager with serious disease are provided with all the support to seek treatment at Patna, Ranchi and Delhi depending upon their problems and availability of treatment. In future a full time Primary Healthcare Centre is  being planned to be established.
                    </p>
